casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Jenny R. ARMSTRONG.
No. D-2844.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 2, 2015.
Jenny R. Armstrong, of Madison, Wisconsin, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
